

welcome page 

    to add the favicon to the website use the site 
    https://favicon.io/favicon-converter/
    to convert a png into multiple favicons for different devices 
    next add this to the body of the head tag 

        <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png">
        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png">
        <link rel="manifest" href="/site.webmanifest">








mx-auto stands for margin x axis automatic which sets an automatic margin for the element in the x axis 
